export function register(){if('serviceWorker'in navigator){window.addEventListener('load',()=>{navigator.serviceWorker.register('/sw.js').then(reg=>console.log('SW registered',reg)).catch(err=>console.error('SW register failed',err));});}}export function unregister(){if('serviceWorker'in navigator){navigator.serviceWorker.ready.then(reg=>reg.unregister());}}
